ram\": \"that title\", \"from\": 478, \"to\": 488}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic gold\", \"from\": 494, \"to\": 506}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kerr, 26, starts his quest with Friday morning's heats, the day afterWorld AthleticspresidentLord Coe, speaking at aParispress conference, branded the impending showdown as a potential \\\"race for the ages.\\\"\", \"from\": 510, \"to\": 715, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Kerr\", \"from\": 510, \"to\": 514}, {\"ngram\": \"his quest\", \"from\": 527, \"to\": 536}, {\"ngram\": \"Friday morning's heats\", \"from\": 542, \"to\": 564}, {\"ngram\": \"afterWorld AthleticspresidentLord Coe\", \"from\": 574, \"to\": 611}, {\"ngram\": \"aParispress conference\", \"from\": 625, \"to\": 647}, {\"ngram\": \"the impending showdown\", \"from\": 657, \"to\": 679}, {\"ngram\": \"a potential \\\"race\", \"from\": 683, \"to\": 700}, {\"ngram\": \"the ages\", \"from\": 705, \"to\": 713}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ingebrigtsen, who won 1500m gold at Tokyo 2020, further stoked the fire on Thursday when he told Norwegian media Kerr \\\"is known as the Brit who never competes.\\\"\", \"from\": 717, \"to\": 877, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 753, \"end\": 758, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9815142654372111, \"rank\": 0.018833890908909096, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 814, \"end\": 823, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norway\", \"score\": 0.9993159848171026, \"rank\": 0.0006751639638565894, \"text\": \"Norwegian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norway\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Ingebrigtsen\", \"from\": 717, \"to\": 729}, {\"ngram\": \"1500m gold\", \"from\": 739, \"to\": 749}, {\"ngram\": \"the fire\", \"from\": 780, \"to\": 788}, {\"ngram\": \"Thursday\", \"from\": 792, \"to\": 800}, {\"ngram\": \"the Brit\", \"from\": 848, \"to\": 856}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But speaking before the Scandinavian's latest barb, Kerr dismissed the clash of big personalities, at least off the track, as \\\"not something that I spend too much time thinking about.\\\"\", \"from\": 879, \"to\": 1063, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Scandinavian's latest barb\", \"from\": 899, \"to\": 929}, {\"ngram\": \"Kerr\", \"from\": 931, \"to\": 935}, {\"ngram\": \"the clash\", \"from\": 946, \"to\": 955}, {\"ngram\": \"big personalities\", \"from\": 959, \"to\": 976}, {\"ngram\": \"the track\", \"from\": 991, \"to\": 1000}, {\"ngram\": \"not something\", \"from\": 1006, \"to\": 1019}, {\"ngram\": \"too much time\", \"from\": 1033, \"to\": 1046}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He said: \\\"I am known to say what's on my mind, and then the backlash is whatever the backlash is, really.\", \"from\": 1065, \"to\": 1170, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my mind\", \"from\": 1103, \"to\": 1110}, {\"ngram\": \"the backlash\", \"from\": 1121, \"to\": 1133}, {\"ngram\": \"whatever\", \"from\": 1137, \"to\": 1145}, {\"ngram\": \"the backlash\", \"from\": 1146, \"to\": 1158}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So, no, I have not really thought much about it.\", \"from\": 1171, \"to\": 1219, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And no we have not seen each other.\", \"from\": 1221, \"to\": 1257, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have been mostly Stateside for my two camps this year.\", \"from\": 1258, \"to\": 1314, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1277, \"end\": 1286, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999999999986358, \"rank\": 1.3412911112138891e-12, \"text\": \"Stateside\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my two camps\", \"from\": 1291, \"to\": 1303}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I like to be in my own zones, and kind of away from as many things within my own environment and stuff I can control, so not too much gone into that.\\\"\", \"from\": 1315, \"to\": 1465, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my own zones\", \"from\": 1331, \"to\": 1343}, {\"ngram\": \"as many things\", \"from\": 1367, \"to\": 1381}, {\"ngram\": \"my own environment\", \"from\": 1389, \"to\": 1407}, {\"ngram\": \"stuff\", \"from\": 1412, \"to\": 1417}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kerr said he has not heard of - nor watched - the Pre-Paris hype video Ingebrigtsen made with his brothers brothers Henrik and Filip, a pop song called 'Ingen gj\\u00f8r det bedre' ('Nobody does it better').\", \"from\": 1467, \"to\": 1668, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1620, \"end\": 1625, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ingen\", \"score\": 0.9999999999663487, \"rank\": 2.948323133442882e-11, \"text\": \"Ingen\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q2566598\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ingen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ingen\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Kerr\", \"from\": 1467, \"to\": 1471}, {\"ngram\": \"the Pre-Paris hype video\", \"from\": 1513, \"to\": 1537}, {\"ngram\": \"Ingebrigtsen\", \"from\": 1538, \"to\": 1550}, {\"ngram\": \"his brothers brothers Henrik\", \"from\": 1561, \"to\": 1589}, {\"ngram\": \"Filip\", \"from\": 1594, \"to\": 1599}, {\"ngram\": \"a pop song\", \"from\": 1601, \"to\": 1611}, {\"ngram\": \"Nobody\", \"from\": 1644, \"to\": 1650}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That's not something I am playing around with at the moment,\\\" said Kerr, who earlier this week was named captain of Great Britain's athletics squad at Paris 2024.\", \"from\": 1670, \"to\": 1833, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1787, \"end\": 1800, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9