": 2115}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Still, he predicted: \\\"I am sure there is going to be some showmanship in there.\\\"\", \"from\": 2119, \"to\": 2199, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some showmanship\", \"from\": 2172, \"to\": 2188}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kerr came out on top when the pair last met in the mile at the Diamond League meeting in Eugene in May for a British record 3:45.34, but their head-to-head record in 1500m finals stands at 8-1 in world runner-up Ingebrigtsen's favour.\", \"from\": 2201, \"to\": 2435, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2264, \"end\": 2278, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diamond_League\", \"score\": 0.9871450361065592, \"rank\": 0.013022365936111308, \"text\": \"Diamond League\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diamond_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diamond_League\"}, {\"begin\": 2310, \"end\": 2324, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Progression_of_the_British_football_transfer_fee_record\", \"score\": 0.9999998230637331, \"rank\": 1.7674408825811544e-07, \"text\": \"British record\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Progression_of_the_British_football_transfer_fee_record\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Progression_of_the_British_football_transfer_fee_record\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Kerr\", \"from\": 2201, \"to\": 2205}, {\"ngram\": \"top\", \"from\": 2218, \"to\": 2221}, {\"ngram\": \"the pair\", \"from\": 2227, \"to\": 2235}, {\"ngram\": \"the mile\", \"from\": 2248, \"to\": 2256}, {\"ngram\": \"Eugene\", \"from\": 2290, \"to\": 2296}, {\"ngram\": \"May\", \"from\": 2300, \"to\": 2303}, {\"ngram\": \"head\", \"from\": 2352, \"to\": 2356}, {\"ngram\": \"1500m\", \"from\": 2367, \"to\": 2372}, {\"ngram\": \"finals\", \"from\": 2373, \"to\": 2379}, {\"ngram\": \"world runner-up Ingebrigtsen's favour\", \"from\": 2397, \"to\": 2434}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He is known as the Brit who never competes And Ingebrigtsen is in fine form after recovering from an Achilles injury, unbeaten since winning the Diamond League 1500m on home soil in Oslo and lowering his own European record to 3:26.73 at the Monaco Diamond League meeting in July for the current world-leading time this year.\", \"from\": 2437, \"to\": 2764, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2539, \"end\": 2547, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Achilles_tendon\", \"score\": 0.9999999773499442, \"rank\": 2.2649838596237413e-08, \"text\": \"Achilles\", \"types\": [\"Q4936952\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Achilles_tendon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Achilles_tendon\"}, {\"begin\": 2583, \"end\": 2597, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diamond_League\", \"score\": 0.9871450361065592, \"rank\": 0.013022365936111308, \"text\": \"Diamond League\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diamond_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diamond_League\"}, {\"begin\": 2620, \"end\": 2624, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bislett_Games\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5404842764054737e-16, \"text\": \"Oslo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bislett_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bislett_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 2647, \"end\": 2662, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UEFA\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5810374757135031e-18, \"text\": \"European record\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UEFA\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UEFA\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Brit\", \"from\": 2452, \"to\": 2460}, {\"ngram\": \"Ingebrigtsen\", \"from\": 2484, \"to\": 2496}, {\"ngram\": \"fine form\", \"from\": 2503, \"to\": 2512}, {\"ngram\": \"1500m\", \"from\": 2597, \"to\": 2602}, {\"ngram\": \"home soil\", \"from\": 2606, \"to\": 2615}, {\"ngram\": \"the Monaco Diamond League meeting\", \"from\": 2675, \"to\": 2708}, {\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 2712, \"to\": 2716}, {\"ngram\": \"the current world-leading time\", \"from\": 2721, \"to\": 2751}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kerr, who collected bronze in Tokyo, has raced just twice since Eugene - the 800m heats and final at the British Athletics championships in June.\", \"from\": 2766, \"to\": 2911, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2796, \"end\": 2801, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9815142654372111, \"rank\": 0.018833890908909096, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 2871, \"end\": 2902, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Athletics_Championships\", \"score\": 0.9999999739625313, \"rank\": 2.6037508489870897e-08, \"text\": \"British Athletics championships\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Athletics_Championships\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Athletics_Championships\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Kerr\", \"from\": 2766, \"to\": 2770}, {\"ngram\": \"bronze\", \"from\": 2786, \"to\": 2792}, {\"ngram\": \"Eugene\", \"from\": 2830, \"to\": 2836}, {\"ngram\": \"the 800m\", \"from\": 2839, \"to\": 2847}, {\"ngram\": \"June\", \"from\": 2906, \"to\": 2910}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He holds both the world indoor 3000m and world 1500m titles, but has yet to enter a 1500m race this year - a fact that led Ingebrigtsen to quip on Thursday: \\\"It is difficult to refer to him as a rival when he is never there.\", \"from\": 2913, \"to\": 3137, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"both the world\", \"from\": 2922, \"to\": 2936}, {\"ngram\": \"a 1500m race\", \"from\": 2995, \"to\": 3007}, {\"ngram\": \"a fact\", \"from\": 3020, \"to\": 3026}, {\"ngram\": \"Ingebrigtsen\", \"from\": 3036, \"to\": 3048}, {\"ngram\": \"Thursday\", \"from\": 3060, \"to\": 3068}, {\"ngram\": \"a rival\", \"from\": 3106, \"to\": 3113}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He is known as the Brit who never competes.\", \"from\": 3138, \"to\": 3181, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Brit\", \"from\": 3153, \"to\": 3161}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I try to enter as many races as I can and I want to be here to entertain.\\\"\", \"from\": 3182, \"to\": 3256, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"as many races\", \"from\": 3197, \"to\": 3210}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Scot explained: \\\"When you are fit, you are ready, the races come to you, and none of the races were the right timing for me.\", \"from\": 3258, \"to\": 3386, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Scot\", \"from\": 3258, \"to\": 3266}, {\"ngram\": \"the races\", \"from\": 3312, \"to\": 3321}, {\"ngram\": \"none\", \"from\": 3339, \"to\": 3343}, {\"ngram\": \"the races\", \"from\": 3347, \"to\": 3356}, {\"ngram\": \"the right timing\", \"from\": 3362, \"to\": 3378}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Prefontaine Mile is close enough to a 1500m where you know what you are doing.\", \"from\": 3387, \"to\": 3469, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Prefontaine Mile\", \"from\": 3387, \"to\": 3407}, {\"ngram\": \"a 1500m\", \"from\": 3427, \"to\": 3434}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I normally come into major championships with one or two 1500s in the season, so we are just playing around with some other distances to make sure that we are ready for the challenge ahead.\\\"\", \"from\": 3471, \"to\": 3662, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"major championships\", \"from\": 3493, \"to\": 3512}, {\"ngram\": \"one or two 1500s\", \"from\": 3518, \"to\": 3534}, {\"ngram\": \"the season\", \"from\": 3538, \"to\": 3548}, {\"ngram\": \"some other distances\", \"from\": 3585, \"to\": 3605}, {\"ngram\": \"the challenge\", \"from\": 3641, \"to\": 3654}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kerr says he has a plan for whatever his Norwegian opponent throws at him, coming in \\\"very well prepared\\\" with a \\\"set plan of what I think is going to happen, but I am very flexible and fluid.\", \"from\": 3664, \"to\": 3856, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3705, \"end\": 3714, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norway\", \"score\": 0.9993159848171026, \"rank\": 0.0006751639638565894, \"text\": \"Norwegian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norway\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Kerr\", \"from\": 3664, \"to\": 3668}, {\"ngram\": \"a plan\", \"from\": 3681, \"to\": 3687}, {\"ngram\": \"whatever\", \"from\": 3692, \"to\": 3700}, {\"ngram\": \"a \\\"set plan\", \"from\": 3775, \"to\": 3786}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not really look at the end image too much.\", \"from\": 3858, \"to\": 3906, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the end image\", \"from\": 3883, \"to\": 3896}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Obviously (gold) is the end goal, that's what we are looking for, but the process is what we are focused on right now, controlling what we can control.\\\"\", \"from\": 3907, \"to\": 4059, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"(gold\", \"from\": 3917, \"to\": 3922}, {\"ngram\": \"the end goal\", \"from\": 3927, \"to\": 3939}, {\"ngram\": \"the process\", \"from\": 3977, \"to\": 3988}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Should Ingebrigtsen defend his Tokyo gold, he would become just the second man to win two Olympic 1500m titles, Lord Coe the first when he did it in 1980 and 1984.\", \"from\": 4061, \"to\": 4224, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4092, \"end\": 4097, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9815142654372111, \"rank\": 0.018833890908909096, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Ingebrigtsen\", \"from\": 4068, \"to\": 4080}, {\"ngram\": \"just the second man\", \"from\": 4120, \"to\": 4139}, {\"ngram\": \"two Olympic 1500m titles\", \"from\": 4147, \"to\": 4171}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That man, now president of World Athletics, said on Thursday: \\\"I am trying really hard not to sort of be really broad-brush about it, but yes, of course.\", \"from\": 4226, \"to\": 4379, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4253, \"end\": 4268, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics\", \"score\": 0.9998478892679135, \"rank\": 0.000152133873222593, \"text\": \"World Athletics\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"That man\", \"from\": 4226, \"to\": 4234}, {\"ngram\": \"now president\", \"from\": 4236, \"to\": 4249}, {\"ngram\": \"Thursday\", \"from\": 4278, \"to\": 4286}, {\"ngram\": \"broad-brush\", \"from\": 4338, \"to\": 4349}, {\"ngram\": \"course\", \"from\": 4372, \"to\": 4378}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's nice to see the 1500m back in the spotlight.\", \"from\": 4380, \"to\": 4429, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 1500m\", \"from\": 4397, \"to\": 4406}, {\"ngram\": \"the spotlight\", \"from\": 4415, \"to\": 4428}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's a sumptuous thought that the best two 1500 metre milers of their generation and for some time, potentially.\", \"from\": 4430, \"to\": 4542, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a sumptuous thought\", \"from\": 4435, \"to\": 4454}, {\"ngram\": \"the best two 1500 metre milers\", \"from\": 4460, \"to\": 4490}, {\"ngram\": \"their generation\", \"from\": 4494, \"to\": 4510}, {\"ngram\": \"some time\", \"from\": 4519, \"to\": 4528}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And there is added piquancy because this is probably not a friendship made in heaven.\", \"from\":